<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Live from the Pasture — Leaning Tree Farm of Oregon</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Watch the herd live from Leaning Tree Farm in Gaston, Oregon. Live pasture cam featuring our alpacas and sheep.">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <style>
    .cam-hero {
      background: var(--sage-pale);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sage-light);
      padding: 3rem 2rem 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cam-container {
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 3.5rem;
    }
    .cam-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      padding-bottom: 56.25%;
      height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--sage-light);
      background: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .cam-wrapper iframe {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: 0;
    }
    .cam-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    }
    .cam-details {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .cam-detail-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--sage-light);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cam-detail-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--sage);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .cam-detail-value {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--bark);
    }
    .offline-note {
      background: var(--bark-pale);
      border: 1px solid #ddd0c0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
  </style>
  <script defer src="/_vercel/insights/script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="nav-placeholder"></div>
  <main>
    <div class="cam-hero">
      <p class="section-label">Live stream</p>
      <h1 class="section-title">📷 Live from the Pasture</h1>
      <p class="section-body" style="margin: 0.5rem auto 0; max-width: 500px;">Watch the herd live from Leaning Tree Farm — alpacas, sheep, and whoever else decides to wander into frame.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cam-container">
      <div class="cam-wrapper">
        <iframe
          src="https://g1.ipcamlive.com/player/player.php?alias=69efd0f9ba4cd&skin=white&autoplay=1&mute=1&disableautofullscreen=1&disablestorageplayer=1&disabledownloadbutton=1&disableplaybackspeedbutton=1&disablenavigation=1"
          allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>
      </div>
      <p class="cam-note">Stream is live during daylight hours from Gaston, Oregon. The camera features night vision — so feel free to check in after dark too. Pan, tilt, and zoom are managed from the farm side. If the stream appears offline, the camera may be rebooting or experiencing a brief connection hiccup — check back in a few minutes.</p>
      <div class="cam-details">
        <div class="cam-detail-card">
          <div class="cam-detail-label">Location</div>
          <div class="cam-detail-value">Gaston, Oregon</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cam-detail-card">
          <div class="cam-detail-label">What you might see</div>
          <div class="cam-detail-value">Alpacas · Sheep · The occasional cat</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cam-detail-card">
          <div class="cam-detail-label">Night vision</div>
          <div class="cam-detail-value">Up to 328ft</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="offline-note">
        Stream not loading? The camera may be adjusting or briefly offline. Refresh the page or try again in a few minutes. For questions, reach us at <a href="mailto:leaningtreefarmoforegon@gmail.com" style="color:var(--sage);">leaningtreefarmoforegon@gmail.com</a>.
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <div id="footer-placeholder"></div>
  <script src="js/components.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
